# QNTMEX Wallet 👑

A React Native crypto wallet app built with Expo featuring a royal gold-on-black aesthetic inspired by the QEX crown logo.

## Features

- **5 Full Screens**: Home, Swap, Send, Receive, Settings
- **Dark & Light Mode**: Smooth theme switching via context
- **Portfolio Dashboard**: Asset balances with sparkline charts
- **Token Swap**: Flip tokens, live rate calculation, slippage control
- **Send Flow**: Token selection, recipient input, confirmation screen
- **Receive**: QR code display with crown mark, one-tap address copy
- **Settings**: Biometric toggle, notifications, currency/network preferences
